# Environment Variables Configuration

## Required API Keys

### OpenAI API Key (for story generation and image creation)
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here

## Example:
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-proj-abc123...

## How to Get API Keys:
# 1. OpenAI: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys

## Usage:
# The system will use these keys to:
# - Generate story sentences based on game descriptions
# - Create images for before/after each game
# - All processing happens on server (keys stay secure)
